Ames.Franklin Township, Story County, Iowa:
Franklin Township is a township in Story County, Iowa, USA. As of the 2000 census, its population was 19,061.
The polling location for the township is the Gilbert Lutheran Church, 135 School Street in Gilbert.


== Geography ==
Franklin Township covers an area of 36.7 square miles (95 km2) and contains the incorporated town of Gilbert and a portion of Ames, primarily the area north of Bloomington Road.
